(present, record the exact location and stop before reconnecting the truck for service.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Brush away dry residue first, then clean surfaces with neutral solution and absorbent pads.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Do not flood the compartment.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Torque accessible hold-down hardware to the approved value on the checklist and replace) Tj
0 -14 Td
(missing cable ties or clips.) Tj
0 -14 Td
