0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Capture battery serial placeholder, truck ID, shift, and technician initials.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- If corrosion was cleaned, note the severity as light, moderate, or heavy and whether follow-) Tj
0 -14 Td
(up inspection is required.) Tj
0 -14 Td
