0 -14 Td
(but shows early connector discoloration near the charge lead. That creates a retrieval target) Tj
0 -14 Td
(for questions about when a forklift may continue in limited service and when it must be pulled) Tj
0 -14 Td
(immediately.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Another frequent scenario is repeated residue near one corner of the tray caused by poor cap) Tj
0 -14 Td
(seating after charging. The procedure should lead a reader to inspect vent cap fit before) Tj
0 -14 Td
(assuming a larger battery defect.) Tj
